Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.79,0:02:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To take back Sanji who was being pressed \Ninto a marriage and left his friends behind,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.50,0:02:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others infiltrated the Whole \NCake Island where Emperor Big Mom is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.67,0:03:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nami and Jimbei joined\NChopper and the others in the Mirro-World,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.39,0:03:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and found Brook who was held captive,\Nto their surprise, in Big Mom's bedroom.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.89,0:03:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After taking great pains, they finally \Nswitched Brook and his double successfully.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.07,0:03:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Meanwhile,\NLuffy was running to see Sanji again,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.03,0:03:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but Big Mom's soldiers kept blocking his way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.58,0:03:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He finally arrived at the \Nrendezvous spot. However...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.57,0:03:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.49,0:04:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure... you'll be...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.74,0:04:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...there!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.70,0:04:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"The Rendezvous!\NLuffy, a One-on-One at His Limit!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.98,0:04:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.79,0:04:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of my way...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.87,0:05:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can barely stand, damn brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop trying to act strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.24,0:06:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard, he can't get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.37,0:06:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take him out for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.83,0:06:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vinsmoke Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.68,0:06:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.68,0:06:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.68,0:06:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.55,0:06:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.85,0:06:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.06,0:06:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.06,0:06:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.69,0:06:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.15,0:06:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you surprised me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.23,0:06:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.61,0:06:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You screamed at a critical moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.61,0:06:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.57,0:06:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm glad that you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.70,0:06:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I thought I was going to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}am{\i0} dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.55,0:07:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When they tightened their security,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.80,0:07:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it was impossible for us\Nto get a copy of the Road Ponegliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.39,0:07:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I pushed it\Nand put you-{\i1}gara{\i0}'s life in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.73,0:07:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.35,0:07:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?\NEverything you did was for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.52,0:07:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like you said, since we were invading just \Nthe two of us, we had a chance in a million.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.15,0:07:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we were to try to get Big Mom's Road Ponegliff\Nsome other time,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.54,0:07:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,an all-out war between pirates\Nwould be unavoidable!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.29,0:07:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we had to try the mission\Neven if it was impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.44,0:07:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, this is the copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:08:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, anyway, Pedro-{\i1}san{\i0},\NI can't believe you got away safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.02,0:08:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Copy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.35,0:08:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.61,0:08:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so desperate at that time too so I couldn't think of\Nanything other than asking you to be bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.28,0:08:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute, Brook!\NDon't tell me this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.66,0:08:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a copy of the Ponegliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a close call!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.79,0:08:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just when I finished copying the third paper,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.79,0:08:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there came, believe it or not, Big Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.63,0:08:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.97,0:08:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was even a Sweet General!\NDid you take down all those guards?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.27,0:08:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Mom's Ponegliff is something that\Nother Emperors of the Sea are eager to have!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.82,0:08:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.54,0:09:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.58,0:09:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.30,0:09:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He got our Ponegliff?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.62,0:09:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.76,0:09:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.26,0:09:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.39,0:09:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Treasure Repository is a room to which \Neven Big Mom's relatives aren't admitted easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.14,0:09:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're something!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.61,0:09:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, could I see your panties...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.88,0:09:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.83,0:09:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His bones got broken again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.78,0:09:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we accomplished one of our goals!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All there's left to do is taking back Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.19,0:10:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be here waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.18,0:10:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're the cook of my ship!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.35,0:10:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...won't eat anything \Nother than what you cook!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.99,0:10:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he's finally dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.04,0:10:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.55,0:10:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if I get hungry or \Nspears rain down on me,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.95,0:10:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll stay right here and wait for you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.73,0:10:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be sure to come back!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.82,0:10:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sanji!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.94,0:11:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.04,0:11:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...be there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.82,0:11:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.\NI'm gonna give you the finishing blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.46,0:11:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.61,0:13:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.12,0:13:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither of them are there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.74,0:13:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--They passed by quite some time ago.\N--They're not here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.99,0:13:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even in Sanji's room?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.83,0:13:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, instead,\Nsome weird guy's sleeping in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.43,0:13:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he's not in his room, where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.88,0:14:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it. I think I know where he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.00,0:14:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's outside so there's no mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.72,0:14:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This morning, Luffy and Sanji-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.05,0:14:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...fought there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.85,0:14:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and Sanji got in a fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.07,0:14:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.65,0:14:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji has his position \Nas part of the Vinsmokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.62,0:14:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must have come here\Nfor a compelling reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it's that \Neasy to take him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.04,0:14:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you wanna get him back,\Nyou must hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.92,0:14:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to tell you when everyone gets together\Nbut the thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.51,0:14:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if they hold the wedding tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.47,0:14:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's not going to be a peaceful one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:14:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.06,0:15:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys came here with Pekoms,\Ndidn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.23,0:15:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Pekoms!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.23,0:15:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he okay?\NWe lost of him on our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.28,0:15:08.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,TURN BACK
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.92,0:15:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but he got involved in somebody's plot
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.95,0:15:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and was almost fed to sharks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.89,0:15:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plot?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we hadn't noticed...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.21,0:15:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he'd be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.81,0:15:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.93,0:15:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...monsters...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.94,0:15:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How pathetic.\NBargirls shouldn't pass out from drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.28,0:15:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish they'd sent us\Nthat girl, Sanji's friend, instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.60,0:16:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! That girl named Nami, right?\NI like strong-minded girls like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.04,0:16:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard she's already been caught by Big Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.63,0:16:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask her if we can \Nhave that girl tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.85,0:16:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, that's enough drinking for today.\NWe'll have a party tomorrow night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.19,0:16:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We Germa will form an alliance\Nwith Emperor Big Mom
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.44,0:16:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and conquer the North Blue again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.59,0:16:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We glorious Germa have been scorned
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.52,0:16:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and insulted by hateful \Ncountries of the North Blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.24,0:16:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The day we get our revenge on them\Nwill come soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.79,0:16:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, we'll celebrate it in advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.67,0:16:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That failure who'd been nothing but the \Nshame of the Vinsmokes for a long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.22,0:16:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,finally came in handy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!\NThe fish that we caught with Sanji as bait is very big!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.16,0:17:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When our enemies see Big Mom's \NJolly Roger on Germa's fleet,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.35,0:17:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll lose their spirit to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.00,0:17:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can conquer the sea more mightily\Nfrom now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.44,0:17:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta thank Sanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.08,0:17:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.96,0:17:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To that failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.42,0:17:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To that beneficial punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.73,0:17:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.30,0:17:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't let the Vinsmokes see anyone\Nuntil tomorrow's tea party.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.49,0:17:42.10,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger. I've already deployed soldiers...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.43,0:17:45.48,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,IN FRONT OF THE GUEST ROOM \NFOR THE VINSMOKE FAMILY
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:45.48,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,...to the medical center on the \Nthird floor where Reiju-{\i1}sama{\i0} is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.91,0:17:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--{\i1}Don't lower your guard.{\i0}\N--Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.40,0:17:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Vinsmokes can't escape their destiny.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.20,0:17:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say so much openly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.15,0:17:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.54,0:18:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.62,0:18:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.89,0:19:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seems like he created quite a ruckus.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is it for him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.49,0:19:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're currently holding\NStraw Hat and Cat Burglar-{\i1}nasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.71,0:19:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy has fought against their top officer all night\Nto get this far!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.78,0:19:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So his body is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.99,0:20:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.36,0:20:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...you said you'd be here waiting!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.39,0:20:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where are you, Luffy?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.87,0:21:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll be here waiting!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.58,0:21:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't come back, I'll be here...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.71,0:21:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...starving to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.30,0:21:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.73,0:23:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After the deadly battle,\NLuffy and Sanji finally see each other again!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.36,0:23:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His lifelong dream and days of \Nadventures with his friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.48,0:23:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will Sanji truly throw it all away?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.50,0:23:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The fight to take Sanji back \Nfinally comes to a climax!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.77,0:23:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"A Liar! Luffy and Sanji!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.13,0:23:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the King of the Pirates!
